      "text": "PHP File Open/Read/Close",
      "level": "h1"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "In this chapter we will teach you how to open, read, and close a file on the server.",
      "html": "<p class=\"intro\">In this chapter we will teach you how to open, read, and close a file \non the server.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
