        "level": "h2"
      },
      "text": "PHP Open File - fopen()",
      "level": "h2"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "A better method to open files is with the fopen() function. This function gives you more options than the readfile() function.",
      "html": "<p>A better method to open files is with the <code>fopen()</code> function. This function gives you more \noptions than the <code>readfile()</code> function.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "We will use the text file, \"webdictionary.txt\", during the lessons:",
      "html": "<p>We will use the text file, \"webdictionary.txt\", during the lessons:</p>"
