      "type": "header",
      "metadata": {
        "level": "h2"
      },
      "text": "PHP Read File - fread()",
      "level": "h2"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "The fread() function reads from an open file.",
      "html": "<p>The <code>fread()</code> function reads from an open file.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "The first parameter of fread() contains the name of the file to read from and the second parameter specifies the maximum number of bytes to read.",
      "html": "<p>The first parameter of <code>fread()</code> contains the name of the file to read from and \nthe second parameter specifies the maximum number of bytes to read.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "The following PHP code reads the \"webdictionary.txt\" file to the end:",
      "html": "<p>The following PHP code reads the \"webdictionary.txt\" file to the end:</p>"
